          </a>
          <a class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg" href="{{ '/donate/' | url }}">
            Support the project
          </a>
        </div>
        <p class="mb-5 small text-light text-opacity-75 col-lg-8 mx-auto mx-lg-0">
          BirdNET is a collaboration between the <a href="https://www.birds.cornell.edu/ccb" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-white text-decoration-underline">K. Lisa Yang Center for Conservation Bioacoustics</a> at the <a href="https://www.birds.cornell.edu" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-white text-decoration-underline">Cornell Lab of Ornithology</a> and <a href="https://www.tu-chemnitz.de/index.html.en" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-white text-decoration-underline">Chemnitz University of Technology</a>.
        </p>
